data.description: Welcome to this newly 2-story listed investment property in Colonies North in the Medical Area. With 4  bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, and 2,103 sq. ft., this property offers potential for a rental  income, upgrades, or a rewarding fixer-upper project. The property has infused modern  style into the space, creating an inviting atmosphere. The chef's dream kitchen,  spacious living area, and a tranquil master suite are just the beginning. Outside, a  private and great size yard awaits your vision. With great schools, shopping, and dining  nearby, this is an investment opportunity with tons of potential that you've been waiting  for.
